                <h4>Our Story</h4>
                <p>Jennifer, the founder of J Briggs & Co, online custom fine jewelry company, desired an improved way to work 1:1 with customers. 
                    After describing her challenges and solutions to her son Wilson, they set out to build a company to solve these problems and improve the workflow of creators.
                     Stephen, the keystone to the entire mission has been the one to work closely with Jen and Wilson to ideate, plan and build a product that meets the needs of DesignVine’s customers.
                </p>
                <br>
                <p>Together, Jennifer, Stephen and Wilson have founded DesignVine, our mission is to provide tools to improve the collaborative process between creatives and customers. </p>
                <br>
                <h6 style="font-weight: bold;">Jennifer Briggs-Jenkins:  Co-founder and Chief Creative Officer</h6>
                <p>A Certified Gemologist, Metal Smither and Jewelry Designer, Jennifer has been the founder and owner of J Briggs & Co custom fine jewelry since 1997. Her passion for bringing peoples creative ideas to real life has been the driving motivation in the founding of Design Vine. 
                </p>
                <br>
                <br>

                <h6 style="font-weight: bold;">Stephen Liriano: Co-founder and Chief Technology Officer</h6>
                <p>A Computer Software Engineer and Drexel Graduate, Stephen is a passionate learner who built our product custom from the ground up. With extensive experience in Software and Defense companies he also loves to get involved in entrepreneurial endeavors, many of which have evolved into successful business making positive change for the outside world.</p>
                <br>
                <br>

                <h6 style="font-weight: bold;">Wilson Jenkins: Founder and Chief Revenue Officer
                </h6>
                <p>A Drexel Graduate, Wilson is a young and driven entrepreneur with experience in Fortune 500, Middle Market, Series A Startup and new ventures. Positions largely focused around technology, sales, marketing and online presence. From a very young age he has been extremely passionate about bringing technology to the creative industries.</p>
                <br>
                <br>

                <h6 style="font-weight: bold;">Caleb Jenkins: Sales Development Representative
                </h6>
                <p>A Baylor undergraduate working towards a degree in entrepreneurship and sales. Caleb has a passion for meeting new people and building relations. He has experience working for multiple small businesses and is thrilled to contribute to the growth of DesignVine. </p>
                <br>
                <br>

                <h6 style="font-weight: bold;">Bernard Santos: Sales Development Representative
                </h6>
                <p>Currently pursuing a Pre-Law track at the Claremont Consortium’s Pitzer College, Bernie is a voracious learner leaping into the world of sales and finance. Having a lifelong joy for writing and research, he is excited to leverage his interpersonal skills and driven personality to help the inspired connect with DesignVine. </p>
